# Rulestead — Project Guide for AI Agents

## What this is

Rulestead is an OSS, batteries-included, Elixir-native feature-flag + experimentation + remote-config library for Phoenix/Plug/Ecto/LiveView/Oban apps. Ships as sibling Hex packages: `rulestead` (core: evaluator + store + snapshot cache + context + rules + variants + explain + telemetry + seams + installer + `Rulestead.Fake` test adapter) and `rulestead_admin` (LiveView admin UI).

**Core value:** Phoenix teams can safely gate, roll out, and explain runtime decisions — booleans, variants, remote config — with 15-minute quickstart, deterministic evaluation, and a calm admin UI that operators, support, and SRE can all trust at 3am.

